description:
When everyone is angry because you are disappointed or upset, you may do strange things.

It's not wrong for you to be that way.

But do not hurt yourself and do not hurt others.

Because when it comes time for you to calm down, you might feel guilty later.

So just stay calm. There is always a solution to everything.

If you can not find the exit, go through the entrance. HAHAHA Good idea right?
